Text.string: My faith is my shield! And so is my shield!
You came to the wrong neighborhood, missy!
You just made your last mistake, blondie!
Always wanted to kill a Siren!
Not sure if you're brave or stupid, witch!
The girl with the mech! Get her!
All right, back to my soaps.
I'll be waiting for ya, Vault Thief!
Go on and run, you little pissant!
Come back! I didn't meet my kill quota!
See? Just a bunch of pissants.
Been itchin' to show that off, huh?
That how you wanna die, rakks?!
This is just like that movie I never saw!
This is NOT what I needed!
Gonna scrap you for the tinks!
I didn't piss myself! That's someone else's piss!
Good! Now it's a fair fight!
Am I supposed to be impressed?
Hiding behind a metal plate, huh?
You need a tank to fight me? Ha!
Couldn't handle me close up, huh?
Just doubled your chance of dyin' twice!
Good trick, but it won't save you!
Double your torture! Double your fun!
Twin deaths for the Twin Gods!
I'm gonna put you down, beast!
Can't do your own dirty work?
Ah, that's how you wanna play.
Come out come out, little man!
Careful! He can shoot through that thing!
What's the opposite of a power move?
I'd be cool too if I had a big barrier!
This power belongs to the Twin Gods!
May your blood water the soil!
May our enemies slip on your blood!
That's what happens when you don't listen to me!
We'll remember you! Somebody write down their name!
On your feet! THIS IS WAR!
We got more where that came from!
This is why I said get behind me!
How's that workin' out for ya?
Tie my shoe while you're down there!
I knew I'd be the one to take you down!
Thought this was gonna be hard...
Gotta fill up with more kill... up...
Be right with ya, Vault Thief!
I'll kill you in a minute!
Looks like you're cruisin' for a dyin'!
Got the pissant right where we want 'em!
The time of the Vault Thieves is over!
We all know how this ends.
More gore for the Twin Gods!
A new sacrifice for the offering box!
Don't say I never gave you nothin'!
A hole in your head, on the house!
Dyin's easy! Let me show you!
Come on, pissant! Show me what ya got!
This is it! This is where it ends!
No! Focus on me! I can take it!
Hey! That's my family you're slaughtering!
Kill a bunch of my family once, shame on you!
The Twin Gods are gonna be PISSED!
Vault Thief's on a tear! Watch your ass!
Think you're real hot stuff, don't ya?
Am I supposed to be impressed? [quieter] 'Cause I am.
I see it... the Great Vault!
Just throw me on the pyre...
Find my shield a good home!
Come and get me, Vault THIEF!
It feels like I'm wearing... nothin' at all!
Bet you'd like to shoot me right here!
Come and get me, pissant! Heh heh heh!
Don't keep me waiting, VAULT THIEF!
I know you got more than that! Heh heh heh!
This is how I work out!
I had something in my eye!
Hang on to this for me!
Maybe now you'll learn your LESSON!
You'll get no mercy from us! [spits]
I'm so happy that I'm waggin' my tail!
Hey, Vault Thief! Kiss my ass!
Kiss my sweet cheeks! Uhh uhh uhh.
Feel the sting of my righteous fury!
Let's get more C-O-V over here!
Got me some backup, aw yeah!
Who's gonna kill ya?! This guy.
I'm the last thing you see!
Oh, real good job there, pissant.
Last thing you'll see... is this pretty mug!
Time for plan B. So I'll “B” going...
Enemies of the Twin Gods must die!
No one messes with the family!
You didn't think it'd be THAT easy!
Gonna be fun for one of us!
Ah ah ah! Not so fast!
Enemies of the God Queen must die!
The Great Vault will reveal all!
Nothin' like a little blood to get your blood flowing!
We are the Children of the Vault!
My life for the Twin Gods!
Take this! [clears throat] Take THIS! Better.
